description:
Reupload of my game for the metroidvania jam that for some reason didn't work for windows but then worked when I exported it to a different folder and it worked.

I really don't get it but I guess that giving folders names like "000AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA" can cause problems exporting games for some reason, I promise I didn't change anything and just exported it, but uploading this so late makes me look like a jamcriminal or something :_:

PD: "a" as a folder name is fine tho
